{"tid":1287324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對今後嘅抗爭總體戰略有少少意見想分享","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:36:56.000Z","uid":261433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc35bcc12bda63c3d4f691d40c26122dabacc3c","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可，係我地嘅核心。但同時要四處亮起星星之火，不斷要佢地岀來滅火。咁對手嘅資源先會分薄同埋混亂。咁樣建制派就要各自疲於奔走，而我地又可以做到真正嘅connect people。記住我地無本錢守城，所以一定要靈活滲透。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求係攻擊上路嘅政府高層。<br />\n<br />\n而對個別議員嘅游擊係中路body punch 將防線引開令頭部不受保護。前日逼到建制親身岀去派傳單就係成功例子。<br />\n<br />\n社會議題就係下路，打佢嘅根基。實質地解決民生問題。証明政府用多多錢都搞唔到嘅野係因為佢地根本無認真搞。例如土瓜灣大陸巴士團，屯門公園滋擾。不忘狙擊蛇齋餅粽令佢地有心理壓力。<br />\n<br />\n只要唔偏離厘三個方向，我估計可以減輕大家嘅矛盾同疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n終極目標係咩心照不宣。<br />\n最後對+4嘅同伴親友致以最深切嘅慰問<br />\n<br />\nP.S.武漢事件我覺得可以借用，但要搞清楚響咩場合&amp;target緊邊個。而個班群眾對我地爭取嘅嘢有無實質幫助。如果只係想7/7個日比內地人返去嘅時候知道同分享返厘單野，我覺得浪費時間同資源。未落車已經比人收曬同禁言。相反將video同文宣擺響建制街站隔離度播同埋藍絲page,可以係一拳打爆肝嘅body shot 。反問建制街站對事件嘅睇法，逼佢地表態！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89605a92235ea4951b23f1ef18625bb876b6defc","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"17e767c4f623c312f6c18b000abc2052f280d100","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6a2d63c7b37dc465f7e093901930ce3f77c1ca77","tid":1287324,"uid":270179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不沉船<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相支援<br />\n（唔妥武漢就印多幾千張五大訴求瘋狂派，唔駛係連登當對方係仇人咁屌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18ea7f1ff795c6c7ecb8220f3a2afbaed9675d93","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0b75424cd7b6aa26f2713e482c0ec7d5c103341f","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e39e2460c0dfe0c19e63509ae8f4bab61b5589f7","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e1ed508cb4f323574efb5d98b46aa9a56cda0cf9","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"51873975dbc50f0c437d87f9b14abb14c21d2a43","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ccbb30c9b7dfa7460d995ac4c7a922d03168958a","tid":1287324,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"29f3c774b00faf43e9b7027bc5e601b26f6c9703","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:28:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5a54709e74ddccd72c6b908f8d19dc5b061ba163","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a0aba0011a1ead100e6006ae09fbbfa6598e4502","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7f03685d36b458cbe4f8cb7a2841333357fea169","tid":1287324,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}